Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.42,0:01:36.76,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}(Dream save us us) a-su, All of us{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.68,0:01:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, explain to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.39,0:01:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.35,0:01:47.98,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\an8}KING COBRA ASSASSINATED
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.35,0:01:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...behind this shocking news!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.98,0:01:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After returning to Kamabakka Queendom,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sabo started recounting about the incident\Nthat took place in the Holy Land Mary Geoise.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.49,0:02:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's an emergency! Someone trespassed\Ninto the Land of the Gods!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.91,0:02:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw Saint Rosward and his son Charlos...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I will save... Kuma-{\i1}san{\i} at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.79,0:02:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.30,0:02:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Only King Cobra is permitted\Nan audience with the Five Elders.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.76,0:02:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.88,0:02:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...Cobra-{\i1}sama{\i} is not in good health.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.01,0:02:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.77,0:02:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Cobra-{\i1}sama{\i}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.39,0:02:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This won't take long,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think it'll be boring to\Njust wait outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to guard Vivi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She's still so mischievous,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.49,0:02:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can't stop worrying about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.53,0:02:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Holy Land in Tumult!\NSai and Leo's Full-Power Blow!"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.71,0:02:53.59,On Top,,0,0,0,,HOLY LAND MARY GEOISE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.52,0:03:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me back the keys!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Sabo, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Jewelry Bonney?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.57,0:04:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know me, that'll save us time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We might have the same goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There are intruders in the guardroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They stole the keys to the slaves' collars!\NCatch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that Kuma-{\i1}san{\i} had a daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always been keeping tabs on\Nthe Revolutionary Army's news.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.17,0:04:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So I trust you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please save my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what we're here for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,--What?!\N--Karasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.02,0:04:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Take these keys!\NAnd tell this to Morley and the others, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you unlock Kuma-{\i1}san{\i} and the slaves' collars,\Ngo straight back to the headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mission is complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.82,0:04:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Sabo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll follow you once I finish my business!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.79,0:04:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. But be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do next, Bonney?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.63,0:05:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go to Egghead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna be okay?\NThat's the World Government's territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to ask Vegapunk how to restore\Nmy father's sense of self!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.89,0:05:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I set out to sea for!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a way to restore\Nhis sense of self?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if there isn't, I'll make him do it!\NIf he can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.45,0:05:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This way! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.47,0:05:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange. I saw someone here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.94,0:06:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, they reduced the number of guards\Nin this tower again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.69,0:06:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though there's so much space to cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.53,0:06:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's mostly because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Saw what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The Lost Chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! Don't even joke about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we're safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.22,0:06:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Egghead is in the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We're heading in the opposite direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I guess this is where we say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.10,0:06:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.69,0:06:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This feels weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.24,0:06:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be so strange if you were a pirate,\Nbut a Revolutionary being so kind to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.08,0:06:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We both want to save the same person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Take care of my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't you know?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's mostly because of that.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Lost Chamber...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you like to ask us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,King Cobra of the Kingdom of Alabasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:09:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Where should I begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The World Government was founded\Nby 20 monarchs...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...800 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,As the creators of the world,\Nthey relocated their families to Mary Geoise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They eventually became known\Nas the Celestial Dragons,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.43,0:09:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and have been reigning over the world\Nfor 800 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside, the 20 monarchs\Ntreated each other equally,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and to avoid any of them\Nrising to become a dictator,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,they intentionally installed an empty throne,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and placed their weapons around it as\Na symbol of the oath that no one would sit there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, in the 20 countries\Nthat lost their royal families,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,new monarchs were selected\Nand have been in place ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, the names of the royal families\Nof the First Twenty...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.14,0:10:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...have been removed\Nfrom their home countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.22,0:10:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But Alabasta was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Queen Lily of the Nefeltari Family\Nhad her name remain in the First Twenty,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.52,0:10:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but she didn't become a Celestial Dragon\Nand went back to Alabasta,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,so the Nefeltari Family still exists\Nin her country.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,For that reason, to be exact,\Nthere are only 19 weapons surrounding the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.58,0:10:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true. But so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.04,0:10:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been reading all the old books\Nthat remain in my country.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All we can know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...is the history written in the literature\Nafter the Void Century.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.55,0:10:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But it wasn't there. Queen Lily's name!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She never made it back\Nto the Kingdom of Alabasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Her younger brother\Nruled the country thereafter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you tell me what you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you want to ask us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,About 800 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that the monarch of\Nthe Nefeltari Family alone didn't live here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But we thought she went back\Nto her country, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.26,0:11:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why she did it and where she went...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.89,0:11:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Since that was a long time ago,\Nthere is no way for us to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. We have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what is the D?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you asking that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, actually, a short letter\Nshe left 800 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.87,0:11:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...has been passed down\Nthrough our royal family for generations...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.16,0:12:27.03,On Top,,0,0,0,,PANGAEA CASTLE
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.83,0:12:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hurting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody, please help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I did-{\i1}eh{\i}! Father-{\i1}sama{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I caught a giant mermaid-{\i1}eh{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.51,0:12:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hm, well done! Charlos!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody, please help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.06,0:12:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no... My dear Princess Shirahoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I feed you-{\i1}eh{\i}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll climb on you and go around the town\Nevery day-{\i1}eh{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi is mine-{\i1}eh{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.91,0:13:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my way-{\i1}eh{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This feels great-{\i1}eh{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.09,0:13:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't obey me,\NI'll give you hell-{\i1}eh{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.72,0:13:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.39,0:13:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! My daddy and all our guards\Nare in the Council Tower...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.77,0:13:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.61,0:13:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.61,0:13:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you mermaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You just said "I refuse"!\NYou're rebellious-{\i1}eh{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.66,0:13:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Asking for help is the height of rudeness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We were turned down by her anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Who cares if she lives or dies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.76,0:14:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are just like wakame seaweed,\Neasily swayed by others!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kingdom of Ryugu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.39,0:14:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You better not rebel against them!\NYour country will be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.81,0:14:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! We dropped our guard, Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.32,0:14:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.82,0:14:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we're here, you're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go home!\NWe'll never come back to this place again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.95,0:14:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Fukaboshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys should go home now-{\i1}eh{\i}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.29,0:14:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep this mermaid as my pet-{\i1}eh{\i}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.21,0:14:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you Celestial Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you do that to our sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll make you pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:14:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it-{\i1}eh{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:15:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Invincible Slave, Kuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Rebecca-{\i1}sama{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.78,0:15:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Rebecca! It's that man again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so aggravating! I won't forgive them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.92,0:15:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Myosgard!\NI can beat him up this time, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'll take full responsibility for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A former Warlord of the Sea,\NBartholomew Kuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.26,0:15:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't matter! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuboshi! Mamboshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.31,0:15:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.14,0:15:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You can kill them-{\i1}eh{\i}, Kuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they're a royal family,\Nwe can buy our way out-{\i1}eh{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially because they're Fish-Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.95,0:15:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukaboshi-{\i1}dono{\i}!\NRoyal families must restrain themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,--Get out of my way!\N--Leave it to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the difference between them and us?!\NMyosgard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Our sister is in trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.67,0:16:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They can get away with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they're pirates\Nand not responsible for any country!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Myosgard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.26,0:16:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you punch me the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.68,0:16:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuma! Kill Myosgard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Tontatta Combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hasshoken Secret Art! Drill Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Leo-{\i1}sama{\i}! Sai-{\i1}sama{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,--Don't do it!\N--He's a Celestial Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Tail Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.04,0:16:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.64,0:16:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Charlos!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They're doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.81,0:17:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be dead! This is murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.19,0:17:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The murder of a Celestial Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The Navy Admirals will come!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Kuma-{\i1}chan{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.09,0:17:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to follow\Nanyone's orders anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go home together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.93,0:17:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.35,0:17:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What is a Giant doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.18,0:17:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Morley!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.18,0:17:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Karasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.14,0:17:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I got the keys from Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,--What {\i1}is{\i} he?!\N--An intruder?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Morley!\NA captain of the Revolutionary Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.07,0:17:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! I'll go down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Son!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me ask you one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the D?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.60,0:18:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave. We have nothing more to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.63,0:18:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Imu-{\i1}sama{\i}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.88,0:18:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,King Cobra is still here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did he say Imu?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Lily...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far I have run{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:21.22,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}doredake hashitte kita noka{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without knowing it, I counted scars{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:28.51,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}wakaranai mama kizuato kazoeta{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A treasure map in my head all along{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:35.94,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}zutto atama no naka ni aru takara no chizu{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still looking for the future{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:42.45,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}mirai wo sagashi tsuzuketeru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The real promise{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:49.16,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}hontou no yakusoku wa{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lies much deeper in my heart{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:56.33,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}mune no oku no motto oku ni aru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:21:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A dream that no one can catch up with{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:21:05.47,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}dare mo mina oitsukenai yume{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.51,0:21:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's all I hold on to{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.51,0:21:11.18,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}tada hitotsu dakishimete{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.22,0:21:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To you who smiles like the sun{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.22,0:21:18.27,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}taiyou no youni warau anata e{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.31,0:21:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll sing the same song as that day{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.31,0:21:25.20,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}ano hi to onaji uta wo utau yo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This wish I don't want to forget even when I grow up{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:32.24,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}otona ni nattemo wasuretakunai{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until it reaches you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:39.71,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}kono negai ga todoku made{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Dive into the Sea of Information!\NThe Punk Records Library!"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.43,0:21:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, I'm Lilith, one of the Satellites of\NDr. Vegapunk, the genius scientist!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.77,0:22:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Edison, also Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.90,0:22:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we'll introduce this one! Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.32,0:22:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Her father is King Neptune of\Nthe Kingdom of Ryugu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.20,0:22:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Her mother is Queen Otohime.\NAnd she is a princess of the Kingdom of Ryugu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.28,0:22:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She was born on April 4th\Nand likes sea grape pasta!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.96,0:22:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,To avoid the pirate Vander Decken IX's\Npersistent proposals and long-distance attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.00,0:22:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,she'd been holed up in a tower for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.88,0:22:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,After she met Luffy,\Nshe went outside for the first time in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.30,0:22:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But Decken threw\Nan extremely massive ship, Noah, at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.27,0:22:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,To keep Noah away from her island,\Nshe summoned the Neptunians to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.19,0:22:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,After her ability to communicate\Nwith the Neptunians was awakened,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.32,0:22:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,she had to take on another name,\NPoseidon, the Ancient Weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.11,0:22:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, she gathered her courage and\Ntraveled to the surface to attend the Reverie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.95,0:22:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Father-{\i1}sama{\i}, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.29,0:23:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If possible, I want to live on land!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.96,0:23:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I just hope the kind-hearted Shirahoshi\Nwon't be used as an Ancient Weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.88,0:23:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.72,0:23:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you've seen it,\Ndonate to our research fund!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.14,0:23:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,See you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.69,0:23:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Surprised by the presence\Nsitting on the Empty Throne,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.27,0:23:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}King Cobra prepares for death\Nas he learns the truth of the world.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.57,0:23:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Facing a cruel fate that he can't defy,\Nhe entrusts Sabo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.66,0:23:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with the 800-year-old secret\Nof the Nefeltari Family!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.91,0:23:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"The Entrusted Message! King Cobra's Resolve"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.50,0:23:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
